Package: LandUsePLN
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Access Land Use Data in R
Description: This pipeline provides access to land use data endpoints. It is designed to be flexible and adaptable 
    to various data sources and formats, allowing users to easily retrieve and analyze land use data for their specific needs.
    The current pipeline retrieves land use data from the [ESA World Cover](https://esa-worldcover.org/en) dataset.
